items.title: Sinkhole Swallows Road in Bangkok After a Subway Tunnel Collapses
items.description: A burst pipe in an unfinished extension of Bangkok’s subway system opened a hole more than 60 feet deep in a road near a hospital and royal palaces.

items.title: Typhoon Ragasa Floods Hong Kong
items.description: Typhoon Ragasa, which caused death and destruction in Taiwan, skirted Hong Kong but brought torrential rain to the city.

items.title: Typhoon Ragasa Kills 15 in Taiwan as Hong Kong Faces Strong Winds
items.description: One million residents of Guangdong, in southern China, were evacuated. The storm left 15 dead in Taiwan.
